HEADWORD: mail carrier
<hw>mail carrier</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person who delivers the mail;
-- also called a <altname>letter carrier</altname>. A male mail carrier
is also called a <altname>mailman</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> postman, letter carrier, carrier, mailman.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

